name: Elaine Hu
description:
Elaine Hu is the Data Team Lead at Flashbots, wielding her powers of quantitative analysis and data science to unravel the mysteries of the blockchain realm. A true analytical mind, she's on a mission to decode the secrets of block chain data and harness the power of machine learning to push the boundaries of data analytics using on-chain and off-chain data.
Before diving into the wild world of crypto, Elaine spent over a decade as a quantitative analyst in the traditional banking.
